snippet.title: Duchess of Impact
snippet.description: We are a team dedicated to amplifying the impact of the Duke and Duchess of Sussex known as #PrinceHarry and #MeghanMarkle. We shine the spotlight on  various causes, people, or organizations doing amazing things for their communities and making a global impact. Celebrating what unites us. Celebrating togetherness, collaboration and community.
